content:
Simplify large group quoting and enrollment workflows with new Lightning web components. Leverage the flexibility to enroll new hires or terminate policies throughout the contract term. Calculate and view employee and employer contributions during bulk and new hire enrollment.

Alert Your Agents When Member Records Require Action: show alerts for policies and claims on the Insurance Agent Console to notify your customer service representative of changes in the records that require action.

Analyze the Customer Experience with Your Service Support: know the current sentiment of an insurance customer based on past engagements with the Contact Center and the sentiment recorded for those engagements.

Complete Large Census Enrollment with an Enhanced Lightning Web Component: use an intuitive user interface to enroll up to 10,000 members, add more primary members or dependents, and update the plan and coverage selections of members.

Create a Unified Insurance Console for Customer Service Representatives: provide customer service representatives (CSRs) a comprehensive view of members' details and activities on one page.

Create Actionable Graphs for Insurance Customers Quickly with Templates: save time when creating relationship graphs in the Actionable Relationship Center by using templates.

Enroll New Hires Throughout the Policy Period: enroll new census members with a prorated premium payment in the middle of a contract term.

Get a Quick View of a Member’s Profile: customer service representatives can view an insurance customer’s profile details on the Insurance Agent Console.

Get Real-Time Calculations of Employee and Employer Contributions for a Policy: see the split between employee and employer contributions while creating policies.

Launch Actions and Resolve Member Requests: use the Action Launcher on the Insurance Agent Console to quickly find and run service actions, such as uploading documents.

Manage Complex Large Group Quotes with the Large Group Quote Lightning Web Component: quickly configure group classes and build, price, and view complex quotes.

Rate Census Members Efficiently with Large Group Quoting Flows: give your customers personalized coverages and price plans at the member level with flows.

Show Insurance Customer's Policy Details: get a consolidated view of all the policies held by the customer on the Insurance Agent Console.

Support Out-of-Sequence Endorsement Across Policy Terms: perform a backdated change on a policy when one or more future policy versions exist.

Terminate Policies at Any Time: terminate policies of primary members and dependents either individually or in bulk in the middle of a contract.

Verify the Identity of Your Insurance Customer: use the prebuilt Insurance: Verify Caller Identity flow to verify the identity of inbound calling insurance members or authorized member representatives.

View Insurance Customer’s Engagement Timeline: get a chronological view of customer activity on the Engagement Timeline feature.
title: Simplifying Large Group Quoting and Enrollment Workflows
